&lt;h1 id="the-founder-visa"&gt;The Founder Visa&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I usually avoid politics, but since we now seem to have an administration that&amp;rsquo;s open to suggestions, I&amp;rsquo;m going to risk making one. The single biggest thing the government could do to increase the number of startups in this country is a policy that would cost nothing: establish a new class of visa for startup founders.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>